children.value: During this unprecedented time of global trauma, I hope that you are staying safe and sane. Ring of Keys is supporting our community by moving our Workshop Series into an online platform. On a positive note, this virtual setting equalizes our Workshop Series to serve all of our Members throughout the 40 cities and 3 countries that our Keys are based. I am eager to see whatâ€™s on the other side of this storm, but believe firmly that it will be a new normal, one that brings possibility and transformation.
